"De er alle inkluderet i dit nuværende abonnement. Gå straks på opdagelse i "
"dem! 🙃"

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To book an lesson, learner would first have to buy some lessons to have pre-"
"paid lessons on their loyalty cards. Then they can reach the website and "
"click the Schedule an appointment button."
msgstr ""
"For at booke en undervisningstime skal eleverne først købe timer, som "
"betales på forhånd med deres loyalitetskort. Herefter kan de gå ind på "
"hjemmesiden og klikke på knappen \"Book en tid\"."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To help you planning lessons without the hurdle of assigning slots to "
"learners, <strong>Appointments App </strong>will expose self bookable "
"appointments."
msgstr ""
"For at gøre det nemmere at planlægge undervisningen uden selv at tildele "
"tidspunkter, tilbyder <strong>Aftalerappen</strong> tider, som eleverne selv "
"kan booke."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To help you planning lessons without the hurdle of assigning slots to "
"learners, Appointments App will expose self bookable appointments. Let's see "
"how instructors can use <strong>Calendar App </strong>then to know their "
"planning."
msgstr ""
"For at gøre det nemmere at planlægge undervisningen uden selv at tildele "
"tidspunkter, tilbyder tidsplanlægningsappen selvbookbare tider. Lærere kan "
"bruge <strong>Kalenderappen</strong> til at få overblik over deres skemaer."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To manage waivers, we take advantage of the <strong>Sign App </strong>from "
"the customer form."
msgstr ""
"Til administration af dispensationer bruger vi <strong>e-Signaturappen</"
"strong> direkte fra kundeformularen."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.homepage
msgid ""
"Transform your driving skills with<br/>our lessons. Contact us<br/>to start "
"your journey!<br/>"
msgstr ""
"Forbedr dine køreegenskaber med<br/>vores køretimer. Kontakt os<br/>for at "
"starte din rejse!<br/>"

#. module: driving_school
#: model:product.attribute,name:driving_school.product_attribute_11
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Type"

#. module: driving_school
#: model:mail.template,name:driving_school.mail_template_43
msgid "URLs Driving C"
msgstr "URL kategori C"

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.homepage
msgid ""
"We offer a 24-hour cancellation policy for all lessons. If you need to "
"cancel or reschedule, please notify us at least 24 hours in advance to avoid "
"a cancellation fee."
msgstr ""
"Vi tilbyder en 24-timers afbestillingsfrist for alle undervisningstimer. "
"Hvis du har brug for at afbestille eller ændre en aftale, bedes du give "
"besked mindst 24 timer i forvejen for at undgå et afbestillingsgebyr."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.homepage
msgid "We're here to help you, every step of the way."
msgstr "Vi er med dig hvert skridt på vejen."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.homepage
msgid ""
"We’re committed to providing prompt and effective solutions to ensure your "
"driving experience is enjoyable and stress-free."
msgstr ""
"Vi arbejder for at levere hurtige og effektive løsninger, så du får en "
"behagelig og stressfri køreoplevelse."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When a customer comes for a lesson paid ahead, it's time to consume it from "
"his loyalty card.<br/>\n"
"          You can book lessons from the Appointment App and make learner pay "
"as follow, or let them book lessons by themselves as described in below "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Når en kunde møder op til en forudbetalt undervisningstime, trækkes timen "
"automatisk fra vedkommendes loyalitetskort.<br/>\n"
"          Du kan booke undervisningstimer via aftaleappen og lade eleverne "
"betale som beskrevet nedenfor, eller lade dem selv booke timer, som "
"beskrevet i det følgende afsnit."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When an instructor takes some time off, you can prevent the booking of "
"appointments during this period."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en lærer holder ferie, kan du blokere for bookinger i denne periode."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When selling products such as packs, this credits loyalty cards which points "
"will be consumed during lessons and exams.<br/>\n"
"                  You can configure those from the Sales / Products / "
"Discounts &amp; Loyalty menu."
msgstr ""
"Ved salg af produkter såsom pakker krediteres loyalitetskortet, hvis point "
"anvendes til undervisningstimer og prøver.<br/>\n"
"                  Du kan konfigurere dette under menuen Salg / Produkter / "
"Rabatter og Loyalitet."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While the document is pending for signature, you can reach if from the smart "
"button at the top of the contact form labelled Signature Requested and "
"Resend the request."
msgstr ""
"Mens dokumentet venter på underskrift, kan du åbne det via knappen "
"\"Underskrift anmodet\" øverst i kontaktformularen og sende anmodningen igen."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.homepage
msgid ""
"With years of experience in driver education, we provide comprehensive "
"training that combines safety, skill, and confidence behind the wheel. Our "
"focus is on equipping students with the knowledge and techniques necessary "
"to become responsible drivers. Each lesson is tailored to meet individual "
"needs while ensuring a fun and engaging learning experience."
msgstr ""
"Med mange års erfaring inden for køreskoleundervisning tilbyder vi "
"omfattende træning, der kombinerer sikkerhed, køreteknik og selvtillid bag "
"rattet. Vi fokuserer på at give eleverne den nødvendige viden og de "
"færdigheder, de skal bruge for at blive ansvarlige bilister. Hver køretime "
"tilpasses individuelt og sikrer samtidig en lærerig, underholdende og "
"spændende oplevelse."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gerne tale med os om dit Odoo-setup eller drøfte nogle spørgsmål mere "
"detaljeret?"

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You are ready to sign your first customers? To do so, open the Sales App, "
"create a new order and the customer."
msgstr ""
"Du er klar til at modtage dine første kunder. Åbn salgsappen, opret en ny "
"ordre og tilføj kunden."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid "You can"
msgstr "Du kan"

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilgå alle installerede apps i din Odoo-database direkte fra "
"hoveddashboardet."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can as well directly create quotes for one lesson without having to use "
"the loyalty card."
msgstr ""
"Du kan også oprette et tilbud på en undervisningstime direkte, uden at bruge "
"loyalitetskortet."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can define your own waiver form from the Sign App, within the templates."
msgstr ""
"Du kan oprette din egen fraskrivelsesformular i e-Signaturappen under "
"skabeloner."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.homepage
msgid ""
"You can reach our support team by emailing info@drivingschool.example.com, "
"calling +1 555-555-5556, or using the live chat on our website. Our "
"dedicated team is available 24/7 to assist with any inquiries or scheduling "
"needs."
msgstr ""
"Du kan kontakte vores supportteam via e-mail på info@køreskole.eksempel.com, "
"telefon +1 555-555-5556 eller via livechat på vores hjemmeside. Vores "
"engagerede team står klar døgnet rundt for at hjælpe med alle forespørgsler "
"og aftaler."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can then grant the learner access to your portal to book lessons from "
"the Contact form, via the gear icon near the contact name."
msgstr ""
"Du kan herefter give eleven adgang til portalen via kontaktformularen ved at "
"klikke på tandhjulsikonet ved siden af kontaktens navn, så eleven kan booke "
"undervisningstimer."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can update the Odometer on a regular basis to better plan you "
"maintenance from the smart button of each vehicle."
msgstr ""
"Du kan løbende opdatere kilometertælleren for at planlægge vedligeholdelsen "
"bedre. Dette gøres via den intelligente knap under hvert køretøj."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"Du har nu gennemført demoens brugsscenarie. Odoo kan tilpasses på utallige "
"måder, så løsningen matcher netop din virksomheds behov."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries "
"&gt; Upgrade your Driving School package and check the related box"
msgstr ""
"Har du ikke importeret demodata endnu? Du kan stadig nå det. Gå til Apps &gt;"
" Brancher &gt; Opgradér din pakke til køreskoler, og markér det relevante "
"felt"

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for Driving School package. By doing so, we have "
"installed a bunch of necessary apps to run your Driving School efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Du har netop installeret Odoo-pakken til køreskoler. Samtidig er en række "
